Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.85,0:00:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,那样子也是啦\N不过还是想当美容师
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.46,0:00:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,那很难的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.56,0:00:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,是那样子呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.16,0:00:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你一定考不上的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.87,0:00:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,那样子说不会太过分吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.34,0:00:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了 好没精神
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.85,0:00:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,受伤了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.18,0:00:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,难不成 没有的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.95,0:00:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.62,0:00:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,肚子痛吗\N不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.16,0:00:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.67,0:00:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,其实
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.21,0:01:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,上课了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.21,0:01:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,起立
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.72,0:01:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,立正 敬礼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.95,0:01:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,早安\N早安 坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.27,0:01:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,刚刚是怎么了\N喂，你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.37,0:01:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,上课了 安静
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.37,0:01:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,石原老师
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.09,0:01:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我为大家介绍新的老师
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.96,0:01:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,石原莉奈老师
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.80,0:02:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,好可爱哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.97,0:02:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我是石原莉奈，是新的实习老师\N请多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.65,0:02:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,这里也是我的母校\N能再回来真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.15,0:02:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.33,0:02:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,莉奈老师和爱丽丝同学是姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.97,0:02:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,真的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.91,0:02:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不要让你姐烦恼哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.68,0:02:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,大家也不要让老师头痛哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.29,0:03:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,那大家安静，开始上课了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.60,0:03:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,石原老师，你有男朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.00,0:03:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,问什么问题呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.54,0:03:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,说一下啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.77,0:03:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.64,0:03:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,老师也在问了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.68,0:03:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,老师也有兴趣不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.35,0:03:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,安静
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.95,0:03:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,那开始上课了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.76,0:03:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,那么石原老师你就看一下吧\N是，我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.13,0:03:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,那打开六十五页
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.20,0:03:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,在这个时期的人类
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.27,0:03:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,所想的社会结构
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.78,0:03:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,人类是怎么构成的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.78,0:04:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,和女友姐姐不可告人的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.35,0:04:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.12,0:04:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么不说你姐的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.42,0:04:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我吓了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.26,0:04:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.80,0:04:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,因为
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.10,0:04:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,自己姐姐是同校老师，好丢脸的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.90,0:04:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,就叫她不要说了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.88,0:04:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.45,0:05:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,有那么漂亮的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.38,0:05:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,而且又会念书，又受欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.62,0:05:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,会被班上同学说\N和你姐姐完全不同的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.23,0:05:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,别灰心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.14,0:05:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你也很可爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.87,0:05:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,真的那样子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.41,0:05:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都那样子说的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.38,0:05:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,那你是怎么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.85,0:05:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,是说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.75,0:05:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,爱丽丝超可爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.35,0:05:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,世界上最可爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.35,0:05:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,不是，是宇宙中最可爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.66,0:05:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.79,0:05:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我在找你，你在这里呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.70,0:05:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下啦，姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.27,0:05:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么在大家面前说我们是姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.30,0:06:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,就跟你说过要保密的了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.71,0:06:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,没法子呀，神乐老师他自己说出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.41,0:06:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,时间不久的，帮一下大姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.29,0:06:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,是 说，什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.39,0:06:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我找下道同学有事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.19,0:06:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,为了校庆的事\N学校说能找下道同学帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.33,0:06:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,请多指教了，会长
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.90,0:06:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.27,0:06:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,下道同学借我一下好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.91,0:06:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,请
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.61,0:06:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,那么麻烦你了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.13,0:07:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.63,0:07:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,这个编在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.49,0:08:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,这个怎么样呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.76,0:08:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.23,0:08:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,应该是编在其它的会较好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.24,0:08:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,那样子呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.28,0:08:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,那么，这里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.28,0:08:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,那样子就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.65,0:08:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,这样子呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.42,0:08:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.25,0:10:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的，为什么不接
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.06,0:10:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.87,0:10:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,好累呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.84,0:10:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.70,0:10:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.47,0:10:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,今天你们做到什么时候呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.50,0:11:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你是指\N你今天不是把下道同学带走吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.34,0:11:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,约一小时吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.85,0:11:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,他真是个认真的好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.55,0:11:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,而且好可爱，帮了我好大忙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.06,0:11:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,明天也要请他帮忙才行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.86,0:11:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,姐你一个人就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.33,0:11:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,而且明天不行 明天要和我在家里念书
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.14,0:11:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.94,0:11:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,明天
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.84,0:11:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,明天
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.64,0:11:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,念书
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.88,0:11:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,念书
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.91,0:11:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,两人一起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.55,0:11:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,不是两个人，和朋友一起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.49,0:11:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.76,0:11:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,那么下次好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.92,0:12:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,真的是那样呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.83,0:12:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.80,0:12:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.87,0:12:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么叫他们来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.61,0:12:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,就障眼法呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.24,0:12:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.59,0:12:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.39,0:12:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,有人回来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.23,0:13:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,应该是姐姐回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.49,0:13:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.49,0:13:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我上一下厕所\N好呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.77,0:13:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.54,0:13:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,这个很棒吧\N你不念书吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.73,0:14:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,好热
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.88,0:16:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你做什么呀，会长
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.65,0:16:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.18,0:16:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,那个，我正和爱丽丝在念书
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.56,0:16:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,想说来上厕所
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.43,0:16:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,厕所在旁边哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.60,0:16:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.90,0:16:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.57,0:16:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,帮我拿毛巾来好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.31,0:16:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.85,0:16:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.08,0:16:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,会长\N是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.05,0:16:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,可以再请你帮忙校庆的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.52,0:16:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,可以
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.89,0:17:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.29,0:17:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,弄好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.37,0:17:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.44,0:17:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,很在意对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.24,0:17:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,昨天你是来偷窥我洗澡对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.32,0:17:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,对女友姐姐这样做，好大胆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.69,0:17:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,老实回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.09,0:18:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.06,0:18:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.33,0:18:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,招认了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.34,0:18:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,这事让我妹知道就不好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.35,0:18:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么来偷窥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.29,0:18:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.72,0:18:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,对老师你好在意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.10,0:18:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,对老师的裸体很在意呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.51,0:18:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.65,0:19:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,那么老师也
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.22,0:19:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,对你很在意的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.39,0:19:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.86,0:19:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,很在意对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.30,0:19:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.37,0:19:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不是有看到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.37,0:19:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,有一些些
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.14,0:19:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,看到了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.55,0:19:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,没有看到吗\N只有一些些
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.78,0:19:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,一些些
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.32,0:19:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,这样子呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.19,0:19:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.23,0:19:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.46,0:19:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,做什么，老师
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.40,0:19:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不好的\N很不好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.87,0:19:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,那停下来好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.48,0:20:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,那个\N有自慰了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.15,0:20:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,那个，没有的\N没有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.17,0:20:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,老师那么没有魅力吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.34,0:20:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,不是那个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.15,0:20:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,没有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.45,0:20:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,只有一下下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.56,0:20:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,有呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.34,0:20:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,被知道的话 怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.57,0:20:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,来做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.27,0:20:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,不好的吧\N很不好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.35,0:20:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,老师 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.35,0:20:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.32,0:20:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.93,0:21:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.90,0:21:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀\N老师
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.21,0:21:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,这么大了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.82,0:21:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,这个是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.76,0:21:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,老师 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.33,0:21:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.40,0:21:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.83,0:21:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不好的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.71,0:21:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,在做什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.52,0:22:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,老师 别戏弄我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.45,0:22:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.96,0:22:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,变得好大了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.18,0:22:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,这里兴奋了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.22,0:24:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,越来越大了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.26,0:24:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,因为
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.35,0:24:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,和女友姐姐做这种事好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.89,0:24:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,没有 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.71,0:25:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,被女友的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.86,0:25:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,摸这个地方好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.68,0:25:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.88,0:25:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,那个是 就
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.55,0:25:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.90,0:26:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.34,0:26:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,舔哦
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.88,0:26:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.28,0:26:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,想要你舔
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.80,0:26:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,想要我舔呀
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.30,0:26:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,那好好说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.41,0:26:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,想要你舔
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.26,0:27:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.70,0:27:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.26,0:28:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,有看到下道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.70,0:28:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.90,0:28:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不好的\N没看到人
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.10,0:28:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了\N爱丽丝她
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.67,0:28:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,在找我\N怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.47,0:29:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不好的
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.64,0:29:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 去找我妹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.51,0:29:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.90,0:29:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.39,0:29:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.30,0:29:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.34,0:30:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,走了哦 这样好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.58,0:30:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,不去找我妹好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.56,0:30:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.89,0:31:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.16,0:31:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,要射了\N要射了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.63,0:31:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,可以哦 射给女友的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.69,0:32:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,要射给姐姐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.56,0:32:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.23,0:32:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,要射了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.14,0:32:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,要射了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.53,0:33:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,明天也来我家哦
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.25,0:33:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.65,0:33:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.72,0:33:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系啦
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.19,0:33:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,这是\N喜欢这样子磨蹭
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.47,0:33:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我去超商一下
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.32,0:34:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我去好了 下道
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.81,0:34:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,爱丽丝 在做什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.46,0:34:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.78,0:34:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你先过去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.96,0:34:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,真的来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.40,0:35:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我妹在家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.41,0:35:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.32,0:35:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,大姐
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.55,0:35:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.29,0:35:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,想摸对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.23,0:36:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,再用力一些
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.56,0:37:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,大姐
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.80,0:37:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,这里湿了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.50,0:37:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,因为你而这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.34,0:37:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒呀
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.68,0:38:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,多舔一下
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.54,0:39:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,大姐
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.32,0:39:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,这里也舔一下
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.37,0:40:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,大姐
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.35,0:41:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,大姐 好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.45,0:41:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服呀
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.22,0:43:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.56,0:43:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,被看到就不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.96,0:43:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,被发现的话 怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.80,0:43:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不好的
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.35,0:44:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,这样子没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.72,0:44:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,会被发现的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.67,0:45:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我和我妹谁比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.71,0:45:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.32,0:46:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,哪边
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.50,0:46:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,大姐你比较舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.81,0:48:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,要怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.18,0:48:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,要进去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.65,0:48:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,想要插进去
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.35,0:48:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,这样子棒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.59,0:48:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,大姐的比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.37,0:50:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒呀
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.13,0:53:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,如何 舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.93,0:53:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服呀
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.62,0:54:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.07,0:56:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.65,0:57:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,看到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.64,0:58:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服呀 大姐
Dialogue: 0,0:58:15.66,0:58:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,插进来
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.29,0:59:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒呀
Dialogue: 0,1:03:19.53,1:03:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,插进来
Dialogue: 0,1:04:32.71,1:04:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,去了 去了
Dialogue: 0,1:04:36.78,1:04:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,大姐 快射了
Dialogue: 0,1:04:43.08,1:04:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,射给你可以吗
Dialogue: 0,1:04:45.35,1:04:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 快要射了
Dialogue: 0,1:06:19.91,1:06:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,这件事要保密哦
Dialogue: 0,1:06:23.50,1:06:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,1:06:42.50,1:06:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,没人在
Dialogue: 0,1:06:50.14,1:06:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,1:06:54.68,1:06:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 老师
Dialogue: 0,1:06:58.15,1:06:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,请住手
Dialogue: 0,1:06:59.75,1:07:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你一直盯着我看对吧
Dialogue: 0,1:07:05.12,1:07:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你看到了吗\N当然
Dialogue: 0,1:07:10.66,1:07:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,1:07:12.77,1:07:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,可是很开心呢
Dialogue: 0,1:07:23.01,1:07:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,1:07:44.23,1:07:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,来做爱吧
Dialogue: 0,1:07:46.63,1:07:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,在这里吗
Dialogue: 0,1:07:52.95,1:07:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,1:08:10.36,1:08:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,1:08:24.94,1:08:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,说有话要说 是
Dialogue: 0,1:08:26.67,1:08:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,1:08:28.91,1:08:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,最近
Dialogue: 0,1:08:31.38,1:08:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,下道是不是怪怪的
Dialogue: 0,1:08:36.22,1:08:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,怪怪的 还吧好
Dialogue: 0,1:08:39.52,1:08:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,1:08:41.89,1:08:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,要说他是在闪我
Dialogue: 0,1:08:47.26,1:08:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,他从以前就是那样了
Dialogue: 0,1:08:50.03,1:08:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,1:08:53.33,1:08:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,没有那回事的
Dialogue: 0,1:08:55.33,1:08:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,他讨厌我了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:08:59.37,1:09:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,最近都没打电话传短信来
Dialogue: 0,1:09:03.38,1:09:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,也没有见面
Dialogue: 0,1:09:07.31,1:09:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我要怎么办好呀
Dialogue: 0,1:09:13.02,1:09:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,别理那种人了\N等一下
Dialogue: 0,1:09:16.06,1:09:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,1:09:17.36,1:09:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会让你那样子的
Dialogue: 0,1:09:22.16,1:09:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.26,1:09:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,1:09:26.43,1:09:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢你的
Dialogue: 0,1:09:31.47,1:09:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,那是不行的
Dialogue: 0,1:09:43.28,1:09:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,太近了
Dialogue: 0,1:09:59.50,1:10:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我会更爱你的\N等一下
Dialogue: 0,1:10:12.38,1:10:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不行的
Dialogue: 0,1:10:13.45,1:10:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,那样子
Dialogue: 0,1:10:17.82,1:10:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,1:10:32.73,1:10:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以的
Dialogue: 0,1:10:43.78,1:10:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,和我一起
