Dialogue: 0,1:35:08.07,1:35:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,1:35:57.86,1:35:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,1:36:04.93,1:36:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,1:36:48.44,1:36:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 不可以
Dialogue: 0,1:37:47.40,1:37:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,1:37:51.64,1:37:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,1:38:21.37,1:38:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,1:39:10.52,1:39:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,1:39:25.00,1:39:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,就说不行了
Dialogue: 0,1:39:30.90,1:39:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,快射了
