Dialogue: 0,1:40:28.29,1:40:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,要射了
Dialogue: 0,1:42:25.01,1:42:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,好久不见了呢
Dialogue: 0,1:42:27.71,1:42:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,今天有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,1:42:30.52,1:42:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,1:42:31.85,1:42:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,这样子来打扰你
Dialogue: 0,1:42:35.79,1:42:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,好久不见了
Dialogue: 0,1:42:40.36,1:42:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,来 请进
Dialogue: 0,1:42:49.03,1:42:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我进去好吗
Dialogue: 0,1:42:52.74,1:42:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,对自己学生出手而被开除的老师
Dialogue: 0,1:42:56.61,1:43:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,和像你这样有未来的教师\N见面好吗
Dialogue: 0,1:43:01.25,1:43:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,说什么呀
Dialogue: 0,1:43:04.08,1:43:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你努力在教师的路上呀
Dialogue: 0,1:43:09.69,1:43:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,1:43:11.82,1:43:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是又诱惑谁了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:43:19.23,1:43:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,像那时候对我一样
Dialogue: 0,1:43:24.00,1:43:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,没那回事的
Dialogue: 0,1:43:28.24,1:43:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,和你在一起时 很快乐
Dialogue: 0,1:43:32.01,1:43:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,但老师和学生的关系\N代价太大了
Dialogue: 0,1:43:38.22,1:43:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,可是 你都没变呢
Dialogue: 0,1:43:47.79,1:43:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,皮肤还是这么棒
Dialogue: 0,1:43:52.70,1:43:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,1:43:54.67,1:43:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不是和老师做了那么多的事
Dialogue: 0,1:44:01.24,1:44:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,在学校的事 还记得吧
Dialogue: 0,1:44:05.64,1:44:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,请不要那样子
Dialogue: 0,1:44:11.55,1:44:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你喜欢这件事的吧
Dialogue: 0,1:44:28.43,1:44:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,一开始的男人是我吧
Dialogue: 0,1:44:32.47,1:44:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我教你的哦
Dialogue: 0,1:44:35.04,1:44:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,有多久没有和你了
Dialogue: 0,1:44:43.88,1:44:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,想要我怎么做
Dialogue: 0,1:44:46.92,1:44:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,舌头伸出来
Dialogue: 0,1:44:48.75,1:44:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,出来些
Dialogue: 0,1:45:12.61,1:45:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,这个地方
Dialogue: 0,1:45:14.71,1:45:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,比以前更棒
Dialogue: 0,1:45:20.45,1:45:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:45:33.07,1:45:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系的
Dialogue: 0,1:45:34.73,1:45:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,来做一下\N不要
Dialogue: 0,1:45:37.94,1:45:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢对吧
Dialogue: 0,1:45:42.17,1:45:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,在学校也有做 对吧
Dialogue: 0,1:45:48.41,1:45:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,这解开来
Dialogue: 0,1:45:52.72,1:45:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:45:56.52,1:45:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,在这里很兴奋吧
Dialogue: 0,1:46:14.47,1:46:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:46:30.66,1:46:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,都湿淋淋了 不是吗
Dialogue: 0,1:46:45.34,1:46:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,乖乖听话
Dialogue: 0,1:47:19.91,1:47:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,好怀念呀 这个乳房
Dialogue: 0,1:47:27.01,1:47:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢这样对吧
Dialogue: 0,1:47:49.97,1:47:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,脚张开来
Dialogue: 0,1:47:59.61,1:48:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,像以前一样哦
Dialogue: 0,1:48:11.82,1:48:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,很湿哦
Dialogue: 0,1:48:32.95,1:48:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,再挺出来一些
Dialogue: 0,1:49:00.01,1:49:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉你色色的味道
Dialogue: 0,1:49:13.79,1:49:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,1:49:21.03,1:49:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,脱下来
Dialogue: 0,1:49:36.11,1:49:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,湿淋淋的哦
Dialogue: 0,1:49:48.40,1:49:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,自己很想要 对吧
Dialogue: 0,1:49:56.63,1:49:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,这样子很不错吧
Dialogue: 0,1:50:51.32,1:50:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,好好来一下
Dialogue: 0,1:51:09.35,1:51:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,都湿了 不是吗
Dialogue: 0,1:51:16.94,1:51:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,很兴奋对吧
Dialogue: 0,1:51:23.98,1:51:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,张开来看看
Dialogue: 0,1:51:30.46,1:51:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,怀念吧 老师的舌头
Dialogue: 0,1:51:35.93,1:51:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,来用一下哦
Dialogue: 0,1:51:49.08,1:51:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,用小肉豆
Dialogue: 0,1:51:55.85,1:51:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,整个舔一下
Dialogue: 0,1:52:38.16,1:52:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,手指进去了哦
Dialogue: 0,1:52:47.33,1:52:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,好好来一下
Dialogue: 0,1:52:52.44,1:52:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,很棒的哦
Dialogue: 0,1:52:54.17,1:52:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,好好看好
Dialogue: 0,1:52:57.61,1:52:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,这样子吗
Dialogue: 0,1:52:59.45,1:53:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:53:43.72,1:53:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吧 这脱下来
Dialogue: 0,1:53:47.13,1:53:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,来哦
Dialogue: 0,1:54:12.15,1:54:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,张开来
Dialogue: 0,1:54:14.39,1:54:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,流出这么色的粘液了
Dialogue: 0,1:54:17.69,1:54:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:54:32.10,1:54:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,像那个时候一样来哦
Dialogue: 0,1:54:47.22,1:54:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,真的好棒呀
Dialogue: 0,1:55:36.07,1:55:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:55:40.07,1:55:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:55:43.84,1:55:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,好好来一下
Dialogue: 0,1:56:28.02,1:56:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,帮我来一下
Dialogue: 0,1:56:32.86,1:56:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,不讨厌对吧
Dialogue: 0,1:56:34.76,1:56:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,来哦
Dialogue: 0,1:56:38.96,1:56:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,帮我来一下
Dialogue: 0,1:56:41.97,1:56:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,来舔
Dialogue: 0,1:57:13.43,1:57:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,用我教你的技巧
Dialogue: 0,1:57:18.04,1:57:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,对 来哦
Dialogue: 0,1:57:23.08,1:57:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,真的很棒呢
Dialogue: 0,1:57:50.94,1:57:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,对 快一些
Dialogue: 0,1:58:14.13,1:58:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃吧
Dialogue: 0,1:58:19.10,1:58:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,多来一下吧
Dialogue: 0,1:58:21.30,1:58:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,舌头伸出来
Dialogue: 0,1:58:46.09,1:58:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服呀
Dialogue: 0,1:58:50.66,1:58:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,真的很行哦
Dialogue: 0,1:58:52.47,1:58:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,蛋蛋也舔一下
Dialogue: 0,1:59:10.65,1:59:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服呀
Dialogue: 0,1:59:36.78,1:59:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,难受吗
Dialogue: 0,1:59:58.00,1:59:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,像以前那样子搞
Dialogue: 0,2:00:00.23,2:00:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我转过去舔我的屁股
Dialogue: 0,2:00:05.72,2:00:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,2:00:24.32,2:00:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,对 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,2:00:35.63,2:00:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,整个好棒呢
Dialogue: 0,2:00:45.41,2:00:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,舔一下后面
Dialogue: 0,2:01:06.67,2:01:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,好好地舔一下
Dialogue: 0,2:01:32.16,2:01:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,对 多来一下
Dialogue: 0,2:01:50.41,2:01:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,来舔哦 对
Dialogue: 0,2:01:54.68,2:01:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,鸡鸡搓一下
Dialogue: 0,2:02:21.74,2:02:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,来用我的鸡鸡
Dialogue: 0,2:02:28.38,2:02:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,用你这下流的手来
Dialogue: 0,2:02:33.82,2:02:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,湿淋淋的
Dialogue: 0,2:02:49.27,2:02:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,好湿呀
Dialogue: 0,2:03:19.83,2:03:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,站起来
Dialogue: 0,2:03:22.90,2:03:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,对 转过去
Dialogue: 0,2:03:26.54,2:03:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,想要老师的吧
Dialogue: 0,2:03:30.78,2:03:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,老师的
Dialogue: 0,2:03:36.78,2:03:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,忍不住了哦
Dialogue: 0,2:03:42.62,2:03:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,可以吧
Dialogue: 0,2:03:51.86,2:03:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,像以前一样
Dialogue: 0,2:04:19.66,2:04:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,2:04:59.10,2:05:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,如何 舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,2:05:09.78,2:05:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,这样子来一下吗
Dialogue: 0,2:05:45.28,2:05:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,要进去了哦
Dialogue: 0,2:05:50.65,2:05:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,2:06:00.29,2:06:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,坐下来看看
Dialogue: 0,2:06:18.01,2:06:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,多来一下
Dialogue: 0,2:06:56.45,2:06:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服对吧
Dialogue: 0,2:07:24.61,2:07:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,好好舒服一下
Dialogue: 0,2:07:47.97,2:07:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉到了吧
Dialogue: 0,2:07:54.91,2:07:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,张开来哦
Dialogue: 0,2:08:21.60,2:08:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服呀
Dialogue: 0,2:08:30.04,2:08:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,2:08:37.52,2:08:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,手往后撑住哦
Dialogue: 0,2:09:10.85,2:09:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒 好舒服呀
Dialogue: 0,2:09:43.18,2:09:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,在这里这样子来
Dialogue: 0,2:09:48.32,2:09:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,说不定会被谁看到哦
Dialogue: 0,2:09:54.06,2:09:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,兴奋吗
Dialogue: 0,2:10:20.15,2:10:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,看这边哦
Dialogue: 0,2:10:22.19,2:10:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,这边来
Dialogue: 0,2:10:29.46,2:10:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,真的好棒呀
Dialogue: 0,2:10:43.28,2:10:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,多来一下
Dialogue: 0,2:11:08.23,2:11:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,如何
Dialogue: 0,2:11:57.08,2:11:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不要 不要
Dialogue: 0,2:12:00.72,2:12:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 不可以
Dialogue: 0,2:12:20.51,2:12:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,真棒呀
Dialogue: 0,2:12:48.30,2:12:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,好好来一下哦
Dialogue: 0,2:13:08.92,2:13:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒呀
Dialogue: 0,2:13:14.06,2:13:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,真的好棒呀
Dialogue: 0,2:13:22.33,2:13:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,想要吗
Dialogue: 0,2:13:27.14,2:13:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,多插一下哦
Dialogue: 0,2:13:30.91,2:13:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,2:13:34.18,2:13:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,整个插进小穴哦
Dialogue: 0,2:13:39.95,2:13:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,用力插我的小穴
Dialogue: 0,2:14:25.80,2:14:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,好好来哦
Dialogue: 0,2:15:13.61,2:15:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,想要吗
Dialogue: 0,2:15:33.57,2:15:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,再来\N要老师怎么样
Dialogue: 0,2:15:36.34,2:15:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,老师 请插进来
Dialogue: 0,2:15:40.21,2:15:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,请插进来
Dialogue: 0,2:16:09.64,2:16:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:16:59.79,2:17:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,要我射哪里
Dialogue: 0,2:17:03.56,2:17:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,射出来好吗
Dialogue: 0,2:17:10.83,2:17:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,2:17:17.70,2:17:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,好好射一下哦
Dialogue: 0,2:17:20.74,2:17:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,看一下哦
Dialogue: 0,2:17:22.41,2:17:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,尽管射出来
Dialogue: 0,2:17:57.54,2:17:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,要射了
Dialogue: 0,2:18:20.97,2:18:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,吸起来
Dialogue: 0,2:18:52.03,2:18:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,要好好当个老师哦
Dialogue: 0,2:19:16.62,2:19:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了 好没精神的样子
Dialogue: 0,2:19:23.96,2:19:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,今天也帮我校庆的事好吗
Dialogue: 0,2:19:27.70,2:19:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,还好吗
Dialogue: 0,2:19:30.47,2:19:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,2:19:39.65,2:19:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,那么这个经费就移到这里来
Dialogue: 0,2:19:46.00,2:19:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,2:19:47.92,2:19:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,再一下就好了
Dialogue: 0,2:19:55.23,2:19:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你的帮忙
Dialogue: 0,2:19:59.37,2:20:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不理我
Dialogue: 0,2:20:02.13,2:20:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了呀
Dialogue: 0,2:20:05.17,2:20:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,2:20:08.87,2:20:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,老师你会在这学校多久
Dialogue: 0,2:20:16.92,2:20:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,到实习结束吧
Dialogue: 0,2:20:24.29,2:20:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,会再回来这里吗
Dialogue: 0,2:20:28.89,2:20:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,分发的学校还没决定的
Dialogue: 0,2:20:34.00,2:20:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,2:20:35.47,2:20:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的是
Dialogue: 0,2:20:40.52,2:20:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,2:20:43.64,2:20:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,想多和老师你见一下面
Dialogue: 0,2:20:52.15,2:20:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,2:20:56.37,2:20:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,2:20:58.26,2:21:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你在这里呀
Dialogue: 0,2:21:02.73,2:21:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么还不回去
Dialogue: 0,2:21:13.51,2:21:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,爱丽丝 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,2:21:14.71,2:21:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,还要请他帮我一下
Dialogue: 0,2:21:19.88,2:21:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,2:21:34.13,2:21:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,可以再帮我一下吗
Dialogue: 0,2:21:40.71,2:21:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,2:23:25.94,2:23:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,2:23:28.94,2:23:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,好喜欢老师
Dialogue: 0,2:23:49.50,2:23:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,2:23:50.40,2:23:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,好喜欢
Dialogue: 0,2:23:59.61,2:24:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,2:24:33.44,2:24:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,好喜欢老师
